### Bank of North America

Not to be confused with the [Bank of British North America](/Bank_of_British_North_America), the [National Bank of North America](/National_Westminster_Bank_USA), or the [Bank of America](/Bank_of_America). One might think, given the sheer expanse of the continent, that more originality in nomenclature would be possible.

